Class Description
AddressBook
The AddressBook class stores methods used to manipulate data stored in the contacts ArrayList

AddressBookSystem starts the program and stores methods which allow the user to interface with the program

The AddressBookTest class stores unit tests designed to prove the logic contained in the program

The Contact class stores the data that forms a Contact object which can be manipulated via getters and setters.

Class to implement Comparator methods allowing for sorting based on First Names
